 <entry>
   <title>Dice</title>
   <link href="http://bsk.education/SE8_p5js/2016/05/11/dice/"/>
   <updated>2016-05-11T16:35:00-04:00</updated>
   <id>http://bsk.education/SE8_p5js/2016/05/11/dice</id>
   <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Let’s say we throw two dice on the ground. What number did we roll?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;script type=&quot;text/p5&quot; data-height=&quot;320&quot; data-preview-width=&quot;470&quot;&gt;
function setup() {
	createCanvas(windowWidth, windowHeight);
	background(&#39;#ED245E&#39;);
}

function draw() {
	strokeWeight(3);
	stroke(0);
	fill(255);
	rect(20, 20, 200, 200);
	fill(&#39;blue&#39;);
	ellipse(120, 120, 50, 50);
	fill(255);
	rect(250, 20, 200, 200);
	fill(&#39;blue&#39;);
	ellipse(300, 70, 50, 50);
	ellipse(350, 120, 50, 50);
	ellipse(400, 170, 50, 50);
}
&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now it’s your turn. We need a 6 to win! Copy and modify the code to make these dice always roll a 6.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
